#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.310" id="310"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an2.310-479:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:0.2"
msgid "19. Rāgapeyyāla"
msgstr "19. Abbreviated Texts Beginning with Greed"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:0.3"
msgid "310–​321"
msgstr "310–​321"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc310.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya dve dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "“For insight into greed, two things should be developed."

msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.1.3"
msgid "Samatho ca vipassanā ca."
msgstr "Serenity and discernment."

msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.1.4"
msgid "Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime dve dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. (1)"
msgstr "For insight into greed, these two things should be developed.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc310.2"></a>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.2.1"
msgid ""
"“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, pariññāya … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya …"
" virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya dve dhammā bhāvetabbā … pe … "
"(2–10.)"
msgstr ""
"“For the complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing "
"… fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go of greed, two things "
"should be developed.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.322" id="322"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:310.2.2"
msgid "322–​479"
msgstr "322–​479"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc322.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dosassa … pe … mohassa … kodhassa … upanāhassa … makkhassa … paḷāsassa … "
"issāya … macchariyassa … māyāya … sāṭheyyassa … thambhassa … sārambhassa … "
"mānassa … atimānassa … madassa … pamādassa … abhiññāya … pariññāya … "
"parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … "
"paṭinissaggāya dve dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"“Of hate … delusion … anger … hostility … offensiveness … contempt … envy … "
"stinginess … deceit … deviousness … obstinacy … aggression … conceit … "
"arrogance … vanity … negligence … for insight … complete understanding … "
"finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … "
"giving away … letting go … two things should be developed."

msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.1.3"
msgid "Samatho ca vipassanā ca."
msgstr "Serenity and discernment."

msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.1.4"
msgid "Pamādassa, bhikkhave, paṭinissaggāya ime dve dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"For the letting go of negligence, these two things should be developed.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc322.2"></a>
#. VAR: etthantare pāṭho sī, syā1-3, kaṃ, pā1 potthakesu
msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.2.2"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.2.3"
msgid "Rāgapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endbook">
msgctxt "an2.310-479:322.2.4"
msgid "Dukanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā."
msgstr "The Book of the Twos is finished."
